00:24:42,430 --> 00:24:44,390
That's why I want to tell him

567
00:24:44,470 --> 00:24:46,580
to look at my age.
I am not too old, but not young.

568
00:24:46,990 --> 00:24:47,990
Why

569
00:24:48,150 --> 00:24:49,100
treat me like a child

570
00:24:49,100 --> 00:24:50,580
and celebrate my birthday every year?

571
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:52,990
Mom, you can't say that.

572
00:24:53,430 --> 00:24:55,260
I know you've always tried your best,

573
00:24:55,260 --> 00:24:56,940
thinking that taking good care
of our home

574
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:57,660
is your duty.

575
00:24:57,820 --> 00:24:59,230
I made this video

576
00:24:59,230 --> 00:25:00,060
to tell you that,

577
00:25:00,430 --> 00:25:00,910
Mom,

578
00:25:01,340 --> 00:25:02,780
your life has always been exciting.

579
00:25:02,990 --> 00:25:05,190
You deserve a good birthday.

580
00:25:05,580 --> 00:25:06,190
Correct.

581
00:25:06,990 --> 00:25:07,820
Alright.

582
00:25:07,870 --> 00:25:09,630
Stop it, I feel so embarrassed.

583
00:25:10,910 --> 00:25:11,580
Liqiang,

584
00:25:11,580 --> 00:25:12,480
hurry, get the knife.

585
00:25:12,500 --> 00:25:13,470
I'll portion the cake.

586
00:25:13,470 --> 00:25:14,320
I'll go get it now.

587
00:25:16,500 --> 00:25:17,780
I envy you so much.

588
00:25:17,990 --> 00:25:19,780
When do you think our two families will

589
00:25:19,950 --> 00:25:21,390
have this kind of treatment?

590
00:25:22,340 --> 00:25:23,990
By the way, Lina, your birthday

591
00:25:24,060 --> 00:25:25,430
isn't far from Yifan's, right?

592
00:25:25,500 --> 00:25:26,100
I...

593
00:25:28,470 --> 00:25:30,300
Yes, your birthday is coming up soon.

594
00:25:30,390 --> 00:25:30,870
Huan'er.

595
00:25:31,060 --> 00:25:32,800
You should celebrate
your mother's birthday.

596
00:25:32,940 --> 00:25:34,060
Just follow this standard.

597
00:25:34,740 --> 00:25:36,630
What? I never celebrate my birthday.

598
00:25:36,780 --> 00:25:37,470
Should we do it?

599
00:25:37,540 --> 00:25:38,230
No.

600
00:25:38,260 --> 00:25:40,740
Here, this big one is for Huan'er.

601
00:25:40,910 --> 00:25:41,470
Take it.

602
00:25:42,710 --> 00:25:45,060
This one is for Hao Mei's family.

603
00:25:45,150 --> 00:25:46,000
Song, this is for you.

604
00:25:46,060 --> 00:25:47,710
Yes, give it to me. He doesn't eat cake.

605
00:25:47,990 --> 00:25:48,870
Try it.

606
00:25:49,710 --> 00:25:51,740
This is for my husband.

607
00:25:52,100 --> 00:25:53,910
Thank you for your hard work.

608
00:25:53,990 --> 00:25:54,580
Not at all.

609
00:25:55,020 --> 00:25:56,990
This is for my son.

610
00:26:36,910 --> 00:26:37,820
Jing Xichi.

611
00:26:37,910 --> 00:26:40,540
What are you doing on my rooftop
this early in the morning?

612
00:26:40,710 --> 00:26:42,100
A typhoon is coming.

613
00:26:42,230 --> 00:26:42,870
These old tiles

614
00:26:42,870 --> 00:26:44,190
on your roof are breaking apart.

615
00:26:44,190 --> 00:26:45,100
So I fixed it for you.

616
00:26:45,230 --> 00:26:46,020
No need to thank me.

617
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:50,090
Why are you coming up?

618
00:26:50,340 --> 00:26:51,390
I want to see the scenery.

619
00:26:52,100 --> 00:26:52,710
You don't know.

620
00:26:52,710 --> 00:26:54,620
When I was a kid,
I always climbed up to play.

621
00:26:55,460 --> 00:26:56,020
Slow down.

622
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:56,430
Alright.

623
00:27:01,710 --> 00:27:02,390
Chen Huan'er,

624
00:27:04,990 --> 00:27:06,100
I know your secret now.

625
00:27:07,260 --> 00:27:08,390
What secret?

626
00:27:11,150 --> 00:27:11,950
How could anyone

627
00:27:11,950 --> 00:27:13,950
wish to be as strong as a bull?

628
00:27:13,950 --> 00:27:14,540
Give it back.

629
00:27:15,020 --> 00:27:16,150
Why did you have such a wish?

630
00:27:19,430 --> 00:27:20,150
Over here as well.

631
00:27:21,100 --> 00:27:21,870
Don't look at it.

632
00:27:21,870 --> 00:27:22,340
What's this?

633
00:27:22,340 --> 00:27:23,380
I haven't seen this yet.

634
00:27:23,460 --> 00:27:27,540
(I hope my parents
won't be unhappy because of me.)

635
00:27:32,100 --> 00:27:33,580
I wrote this when I was a kid.

636
00:27:36,670 --> 00:27:37,630
Then your wish

637
00:27:38,060 --> 00:27:39,060
has come true, it seems.

638
00:27:43,230 --> 00:27:44,260
My grandpa is right.

639
00:27:44,340 --> 00:27:45,390
Just write down your wish

640
00:27:45,390 --> 00:27:47,230
on the tiles, and they will be realized.

641
00:27:51,230 --> 00:27:51,950
Hold on.

642
00:27:52,840 --> 00:27:53,870
What do you want to do?

643
00:27:54,060 --> 00:27:54,870
Slow down.

644
00:27:55,470 --> 00:27:56,230
Be careful.

645
00:27:56,230 --> 00:27:57,780
This ladder isn't very solid.

646
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:59,100
I've repaired this ladder, too.

647
00:28:00,460 --> 00:28:00,990
Wait for me.

648
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:02,430
What are you going to do?

649
00:28:02,630 --> 00:28:03,430
You'll see.

650
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:37,740
Why did you write so many wishes?

651
00:28:37,820 --> 00:28:39,430
It's rude to look at other's wishes.

652
00:28:40,150 --> 00:28:41,540
Didn't you write a lot, too?

653
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:42,880
Writing wishes is free anyway.

654
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:44,090
Just write as many as possible.

655
00:28:44,260 --> 00:28:45,480
Let me see what you wrote.

656
00:28:45,580 --> 00:28:46,340
Nothing.

657
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:47,580
Okay.

658
00:28:47,580 --> 00:28:49,040
Let's not look at each other's wishes.

659
00:28:49,040 --> 00:28:50,430
Cheapskate.

660
00:28:51,340 --> 00:28:51,870
By the way,

661
00:28:52,060 --> 00:28:53,540
you didn't tell me

662
00:28:53,540 --> 00:28:55,060
about Aunt Lin's birthday surprise.

663
00:28:55,470 --> 00:28:57,230
Why so mysterious? Aren't we buddies?

664
00:28:58,340 --> 00:28:59,470
What is a surprise?

665
00:28:59,780 --> 00:29:01,420
What's the point in telling you ahead?

666
00:29:01,430 --> 00:29:02,100
Let me tell you.

667
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:03,580
On the outside, my mom

668
00:29:03,580 --> 00:29:04,780
looks gentle and mild-mannered.

669
00:29:04,910 --> 00:29:05,540
She always says

670
00:29:05,950 --> 00:29:06,910
it's too much trouble

671
00:29:06,990 --> 00:29:08,710
to celebrate her birthday at this age.

672
00:29:09,020 --> 00:29:09,990
But if you prepare

673
00:29:09,990 --> 00:29:10,990
a surprise for her,

674
00:29:10,990 --> 00:29:12,180
she will still be very happy.

675
00:29:14,060 --> 00:29:14,630
True.

676
00:29:15,340 --> 00:29:15,950
By the way,

677
00:29:16,470 --> 00:29:18,950
do you celebrate your mom's birthday
every year?

678
00:29:20,780 --> 00:29:22,920
The celebration this year
is considered low-key.

679
00:29:23,100 --> 00:29:23,990
What about last year?

680
00:29:25,260 --> 00:29:27,910
It was more high-profile last year.

681
00:29:28,950 --> 00:29:29,950
How so?

682
00:29:32,190 --> 00:29:33,060
Jing Xichi.

683
00:29:34,500 --> 00:29:36,020
Happy birthday, Mom.

684
00:29:36,020 --> 00:29:39,340
(Happy birthday, Dear Ms. Lin Yifan!)

685
00:29:42,150 --> 00:29:44,380
What are you doing?

686
00:29:44,430 --> 00:29:46,540
- Ms. Lin.
- Happy birthday.

687
00:29:46,870 --> 00:29:48,190
Are there any cakes?

688
00:29:48,260 --> 00:29:49,300
- Yes.
- Let me have some.

689
00:29:49,300 --> 00:29:50,780
Ms. Lin, are there any cakes for us?

690
00:29:55,780 --> 00:29:57,000
Anyway, she prohibited me

691
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:58,820
from going to the hospital
for over six months.

692
00:29:58,820 --> 00:30:00,300
She must've been very angry.

693
00:30:00,430 --> 00:30:01,780
She's just stubborn.

694
00:30:02,500 --> 00:30:04,100
Anyway, it just has to be memorable.

695
00:30:04,340 --> 00:30:05,190
I have to let my mom

696
00:30:05,190 --> 00:30:06,430
know on her birthday

697
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:08,760
that she is the most important person
in my heart.

698
00:30:10,670 --> 00:30:11,540
So,

699
00:30:11,910 --> 00:30:14,470
what mothers say

700
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:15,990
is not necessarily true.

701
00:30:38,280 --> 00:30:40,870
Didn't you say that we shouldn't
look at each other's wishes?

702
00:30:41,100 --> 00:30:41,780
No.

703
00:30:41,780 --> 00:30:42,340
Let me see.

704
00:30:42,340 --> 00:30:43,060
You'll know later.

705
00:30:43,060 --> 00:30:43,800
Don't be so stingy.

706
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:45,020
No, it won't work if you see it.

707
00:30:45,020 --> 00:30:45,630
Just this once.

708
00:30:45,820 --> 00:30:47,100
No, absolutely not.

709
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:48,440
It won't work after you see it.

710
00:32:10,300 --> 00:32:10,780
Mom.

711
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:13,160
Why don't you want to
celebrate your birthday?

712
00:32:13,580 --> 00:32:14,540
What birthday?

713
00:32:14,580 --> 00:32:16,100
It's just another year passing away.

714
00:32:16,990 --> 00:32:17,990
We will just have a meal.

715
00:32:18,060 --> 00:32:19,340
Don't make a big fuss over it.

716
00:32:24,060 --> 00:32:24,990
So,

717
00:32:25,390 --> 00:32:26,340
what mothers

718
00:32:26,630 --> 00:32:27,910
say sometimes

719
00:32:28,260 --> 00:32:29,390
is not necessarily true.

720
00:32:42,670 --> 00:32:43,230
Hey, girl.

721
00:32:43,710 --> 00:32:44,780
Dad, are you busy?

722
00:32:45,950 --> 00:32:47,470
Do you have the time

723
00:32:47,500 --> 00:32:48,960
to take a vacation and come home?

724
00:32:49,150 --> 00:32:49,740
What's wrong?

725
00:32:50,540 --> 00:32:52,260
Isn't my mom's birthday coming soon?

726
00:32:52,340 --> 00:32:53,670
I thinking of celebrating it

727
00:32:53,990 --> 00:32:55,060
with you.

728
00:32:55,910 --> 00:32:56,630
Oh, is that so?

729
00:32:57,480 --> 00:32:59,580
We have been practicing
for the competition recently.

730
00:32:59,580 --> 00:33:00,320
It's hard to say.

731
00:33:02,260 --> 00:33:03,340
Okay, I understand.

732
00:33:06,710 --> 00:33:07,390
I understand.

733
00:33:41,230 --> 00:33:43,150
So you just don't want to help.

734
00:33:43,180 --> 00:33:46,100
Didn't you say I am a one-trick pony
who only knows how to make videos?

735
00:33:46,340 --> 00:33:47,500
Why ask me for help then?

736
00:33:47,820 --> 00:33:48,910
That's enough.

737
00:33:48,910 --> 00:33:49,430
Shut up.

738
00:33:55,300 --> 00:33:56,990
I'm wrong and I'm sorry.

739
00:34:04,990 --> 00:34:05,820
Big Brother.

740
00:34:12,540 --> 00:34:13,580
Louder.

741
00:34:17,270 --> 00:34:18,220
Big Brother.

742
00:34:20,700 --> 00:34:21,350
What is it?

743
00:34:21,990 --> 00:34:24,270
I just want to celebrate
my mom's birthday.

744
00:34:24,500 --> 00:34:25,500
I don't have any pictures

745
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:26,790
of my mom in the album.

746
00:34:27,430 --> 00:34:28,990
I want to ask you for your help.

747
00:34:30,500 --> 00:34:31,470
Then I guess

748
00:34:31,990 --> 00:34:33,750
I have no choice but to help you.

749
00:34:33,820 --> 00:34:34,990
Thank you, Big Brother.

750
00:34:35,390 --> 00:34:37,180
Anyway, I saw all the pictures.

751
00:34:37,540 --> 00:34:39,500
I remember that there are
pictures of Aunt Lina.

752
00:34:39,560 --> 00:34:40,180
Really?

753
00:34:40,310 --> 00:34:40,620
Where?

754
00:34:40,620 --> 00:34:41,840
It should be in Song's album.

755
00:34:42,140 --> 00:34:42,990
I'll find it.

756
00:34:45,700 --> 00:34:46,270
Where is it?

757
00:34:46,700 --> 00:34:47,470
Isn't this the one?

758
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:52,470
So pretty.

759
00:34:52,540 --> 00:34:54,180
When I saw it, I thought

760
00:34:54,700 --> 00:34:56,790
Uncle Song and Aunt Lina

761
00:34:56,910 --> 00:34:57,790
were quite close.

762
00:34:57,940 --> 00:34:59,780
There are many photos
of them together.

763
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:00,470
Really?

764
00:35:01,310 --> 00:35:02,910
Your dad must have taken this photo.

765
00:35:07,830 --> 00:35:09,390
When I saw it,

766
00:35:09,950 --> 00:35:10,990
I thought,

767
00:35:10,990 --> 00:35:12,390
your dad and your mom's relationship

768
00:35:12,430 --> 00:35:13,540
must be extraordinary.

769
00:35:14,580 --> 00:35:15,910
Now when I see this photo,

770
00:35:15,910 --> 00:35:16,750
I feel like...

771
00:35:28,620 --> 00:35:30,020
I have discovered

772
00:35:30,020 --> 00:35:31,100
something incredible.

773
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:33,910
Although it's hard to believe,

774
00:35:33,990 --> 00:35:35,270
don't dismiss me first.

775
00:35:36,060 --> 00:35:37,140
Let me analyze it for you.

776
00:35:37,910 --> 00:35:38,700
Aunt Lina

777
00:35:39,180 --> 00:35:40,660
was smiling so happily

778
00:35:41,270 --> 00:35:42,220
and brilliantly.

779
00:35:42,620 --> 00:35:43,390
The love in her eyes

780
00:35:43,390 --> 00:35:44,790
is overflowing.

781
00:35:51,580 --> 00:35:52,540
Fortunately, that year,

782
00:35:52,540 --> 00:35:54,180
your dad and your mom weren't together.

783
00:35:56,470 --> 00:35:57,180
Otherwise,

784
00:35:57,180 --> 00:35:58,310
I'd lose two close friends.

785
00:35:58,620 --> 00:35:59,540
I would be the only kid

786
00:35:59,600 --> 00:36:00,960
in this family housing compound.

787
00:36:01,180 --> 00:36:01,950
Jing Xichi.

788
00:36:01,950 --> 00:36:03,180
Are you sick?

789
00:36:03,180 --> 00:36:05,020
If you are sick, go see a doctor.

790
00:36:05,350 --> 00:36:06,620
You two don't believe me?

791
00:36:07,220 --> 00:36:08,700
There is concrete evidence.

792
00:36:09,660 --> 00:36:10,580
Come here.

793
00:36:10,700 --> 00:36:11,500
Take a closer look.

794
00:36:26,700 --> 00:36:27,790
Have you finished shooting?

795
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:29,220
I'm done.

796
00:36:31,830 --> 00:36:32,660
Does it look good?

797
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:33,700
Of course.

798
00:36:34,870 --> 00:36:35,750
You are pretty.

799
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:37,520
You're photogenic
no matter how I take it.

800
00:36:37,870 --> 00:36:39,430
Okay, I will get it from you later.

801
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,340
No need for that.

802
00:36:40,380 --> 00:36:41,500
After I develop the photos,

803
00:36:41,500 --> 00:36:43,040
I will send them to your department.

804
00:36:43,060 --> 00:36:43,900
Thank you, Song Hang.

805
00:36:45,830 --> 00:36:46,390
Yifan,

806
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:48,420
let me take some for you as well.

807
00:37:18,750 --> 00:37:19,830
Look at this girl.

808
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:21,350
Doesn't she look like Huan'er?

809
00:37:21,470 --> 00:37:21,950
Song Hang.

810
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:25,220
There's some resemblance.

811
00:37:26,790 --> 00:37:27,910
I think if Huan'er

812
00:37:27,990 --> 00:37:29,180
dresses up a little,

813
00:37:29,220 --> 00:37:30,780
she wouldn't lose to these actresses.

814
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:33,120
Exactly. I think Huan'er
just needs to dress up a little.

815
00:37:33,120 --> 00:37:34,420
Actually, her facial features

816
00:37:34,700 --> 00:37:36,180
are pretty nice.

817
00:37:36,470 --> 00:37:37,620
Exactly.

818
00:37:38,140 --> 00:37:39,140
She's just like Lina.

819
00:37:39,500 --> 00:37:41,350
Born with good looks, she'll be fine.

820
00:37:43,270 --> 00:37:44,790
Lina is the prettier one, isn't she?

821
00:37:45,870 --> 00:37:46,830
Do still you miss her?

822
00:37:46,910 --> 00:37:47,950
What are you saying?

823
00:37:48,060 --> 00:37:49,140
Our son is here.

824
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:55,950
What's wrong?

825
00:37:58,830 --> 00:37:59,660
Nothing.

826
00:38:00,390 --> 00:38:00,830
I'm fine.

827
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:02,470
Have a kumquat.

828
00:38:08,870 --> 00:38:09,500
What's wrong?

829
00:38:15,910 --> 00:38:16,540
It's sour.

830
00:38:17,430 --> 00:38:18,390
Has it gone bad?

831
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:24,180
It's not sour.

832
00:38:39,870 --> 00:38:40,430
Photo.

833
00:38:41,990 --> 00:38:42,620
Photo?

834
00:38:48,270 --> 00:38:49,660
You really enlarged it.

835
00:38:50,020 --> 00:38:51,100
How did you do it?

836
00:38:51,100 --> 00:38:52,790
The guys at the photo studio did it.

837
00:38:52,990 --> 00:38:54,390
They must have their own ways.

838
00:38:55,660 --> 00:38:56,220
Look.

839
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:58,350
Look at this picture of my mom.

840
00:38:58,790 --> 00:38:59,790
She is so beautiful.

841
00:38:59,820 --> 00:39:00,890
She was dressed colorfully.

842
00:39:00,940 --> 00:39:01,860
Wearing a big earring.

843
00:39:01,870 --> 00:39:02,790
When my mom told me,

844
00:39:02,790 --> 00:39:03,760
I didn't believe her.

845
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:06,540
I saw a lot of photos
when I was going over them.

846
00:39:06,540 --> 00:39:07,950
You haven't seen Aunt Hao yet.

847
00:39:08,440 --> 00:39:09,350
When they were young,

848
00:39:09,350 --> 00:39:10,660
they wore many matching outfits.

849
00:39:11,140 --> 00:39:11,870
Really?

850
00:39:18,310 --> 00:39:19,140
What a pity.

851
00:39:20,310 --> 00:39:22,060
They don't dress up much now.

852
00:39:23,020 --> 00:39:24,430
My mother always says

853
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:26,760
there is no need to dress up
after becoming a mother.

854
00:39:29,390 --> 00:39:31,790
Everyone says time kills beauty.

855
00:39:32,390 --> 00:39:33,500
I think

856
00:39:34,350 --> 00:39:36,060
my parents' youth was stolen

857
00:39:36,350 --> 00:39:37,270
by us

858
00:39:38,100 --> 00:39:38,990
not the years.

859
00:39:45,470 --> 00:39:46,220
When I was a kid,

860
00:39:46,220 --> 00:39:47,910
I liked to browse our photo albums.

861
00:39:48,950 --> 00:39:50,220
Then I thought

862
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,350
my parents in the photos

863
00:39:51,350 --> 00:39:52,870
looked really energetic.

864
00:39:53,350 --> 00:39:55,180
I just wanted to grow up quickly

865
00:39:55,540 --> 00:39:56,950
and become the same as them.

866
00:39:58,270 --> 00:39:58,870
Chen Huan'er,

867
00:39:59,790 --> 00:40:01,350
when we become parents,

868
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:02,740
will this happen to us, too?

869
00:40:07,660 --> 00:40:08,430
Us?

870
00:40:09,220 --> 00:40:10,470
Becoming parents?

871
00:40:19,660 --> 00:40:20,220
No.

872
00:40:20,910 --> 00:40:23,620
I mean when we both...

873
00:40:24,620 --> 00:40:25,180
Not really.

874
00:40:25,910 --> 00:40:27,140
Have you ordered the cake?

875
00:40:28,140 --> 00:40:29,790
When I ordered the cake two days ago,

876
00:40:29,870 --> 00:40:31,270
they gave me a coupon.

877
00:40:31,310 --> 00:40:31,980
Do you want it?

878
00:40:32,080 --> 00:40:33,470
Why didn't you say it earlier?

879
00:40:33,470 --> 00:40:34,540
I'll look for it.

880
00:40:36,700 --> 00:40:37,470
Over here.

881
00:40:37,500 --> 00:40:37,830
Right.

882
00:40:37,870 --> 00:40:38,270
This one.

883
00:40:38,910 --> 00:40:39,430
Thanks.

884
00:40:40,540 --> 00:40:43,580
(Popular Recommendation)

885
00:40:46,660 --> 00:40:48,020
This looks so good.

886
00:40:50,350 --> 00:40:51,700
Must be delicious.

887
00:40:52,100 --> 00:40:53,020
It does look good.

888
00:40:53,860 --> 00:40:55,350
But it should be quite expensive.

889
00:40:58,080 --> 00:40:59,580
Let's go in and take a look first.

890
00:41:00,221 --> 00:41:03,660
(Popular Recommendation)

891
00:41:03,660 --> 00:41:04,350
Hello there.

892
00:41:05,470 --> 00:41:06,100
Hello.

893
00:41:06,500 --> 00:41:07,910
I ordered a cake from here.

894
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:09,580
It was ordered by my dad.

895
00:41:09,700 --> 00:41:10,750
I want to pay for it.

896
00:41:10,950 --> 00:41:12,270
Hold on, let me check.

897
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:14,100
Did Uncle Chen order it?

898
00:41:14,830 --> 00:41:15,950
I thought you ordered it.

899
00:41:16,500 --> 00:41:17,500
Last night, my dad

900
00:41:17,500 --> 00:41:18,950
sent me a message.

901
00:41:19,180 --> 00:41:20,470
I was quite surprised.

902
00:41:21,060 --> 00:41:22,140
Maybe

903
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:23,500
he feels guilty for not coming.

904
00:41:24,040 --> 00:41:25,310
Actually, it doesn't matter.

905
00:41:25,350 --> 00:41:26,720
It doesn't matter who orders it.

906
00:41:27,470 --> 00:41:28,620
Just checking with you.

907
00:41:29,140 --> 00:41:31,540
(Fantasy Princess)
You have ordered the Fantasy Princess.

908
00:41:31,580 --> 00:41:32,240
Am I right?

909
00:41:33,020 --> 00:41:33,660
This one?

910
00:41:34,270 --> 00:41:34,700
Yes.

911
00:41:35,860 --> 00:41:37,390
It seems like in Uncle Chen's eyes

912
00:41:37,390 --> 00:41:39,740
Aunt Lina is still a little princess.

913
00:41:41,060 --> 00:41:42,140
Why do I think

914
00:41:45,020 --> 00:41:46,830
it's kind of lame?

915
00:41:48,580 --> 00:41:50,750
It's alright. Look.

916
00:41:50,830 --> 00:41:51,800
It's all pink and tender.

917
00:41:51,870 --> 00:41:52,940
Colorful.

918
00:41:53,040 --> 00:41:53,870
Vibrant.

919
00:41:54,620 --> 00:41:55,470
It is a little lame.

920
00:41:55,950 --> 00:41:56,620
Right?

921
00:42:01,380 --> 00:42:03,100
Sorry, can I switch to this one instead?

922
00:42:03,180 --> 00:42:04,040
This one looks good.

923
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:04,740
Better than that.

924
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:05,780
I want to order this one.

925
00:42:05,860 --> 00:42:06,340
Sure.

926
00:42:06,620 --> 00:42:08,270
Just to be sure,

927
00:42:08,500 --> 00:42:11,350
you'll collect it at 5 PM
on the day after tomorrow, right?

928
00:42:11,700 --> 00:42:12,100
Yes.

929
00:42:12,390 --> 00:42:12,830
Okay.

930
00:42:13,100 --> 00:42:13,700
68.

931
00:42:14,020 --> 00:42:14,660
68.

932
00:42:15,470 --> 00:42:17,790
I have a coupon.

933
00:42:17,840 --> 00:42:18,950
Can you give me a discount?

934
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:19,660
Sure.

935
00:42:25,790 --> 00:42:26,750
Here, hold on to this.

936
00:42:27,020 --> 00:42:27,620
Thanks.

937
00:42:27,870 --> 00:42:28,390
It's okay.

938
00:42:28,470 --> 00:42:28,990
Excuse me.

939
00:42:29,180 --> 00:42:31,140
That cake on the display...

940
00:42:31,310 --> 00:42:32,700
Do you sell it in slices?

941
00:42:33,270 --> 00:42:34,140
I'm sorry.

942
00:42:34,470 --> 00:42:36,310
We only sell it whole.

943
00:42:36,430 --> 00:42:37,220
No slices.

944
00:42:38,950 --> 00:42:39,500
Okay.

945
00:42:40,620 --> 00:42:41,060
Let's go.

946
00:42:41,830 --> 00:42:42,500
Thanks.

947
00:42:43,260 --> 00:42:46,140
(Popular Recommendation)

948
00:42:57,100 --> 00:42:58,700
If you really like it,

949
00:42:59,500 --> 00:43:00,750
let's check out another store?

950
00:43:01,750 --> 00:43:03,470
No, I'm just looking.

951
00:43:29,961 --> 00:43:35,131
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

952
00:43:36,921 --> 00:43:42,001
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

953
00:43:43,771 --> 00:43:49,121
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

954
00:43:49,431 --> 00:43:54,921
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

955
00:43:57,511 --> 00:44:02,531
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

956
00:44:04,321 --> 00:44:09,561
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

957
00:44:11,161 --> 00:44:16,581
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

958
00:44:17,041 --> 00:44:22,541
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

959
00:44:23,741 --> 00:44:27,701
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

960
00:44:27,701 --> 00:44:32,691
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

961
00:44:32,821 --> 00:44:36,251
♪And full of life♪

962
00:44:37,541 --> 00:44:41,001
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

963
00:44:41,001 --> 00:44:46,111
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

964
00:44:46,371 --> 00:44:50,761
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

965
00:44:51,261 --> 00:44:55,161
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

966
00:44:55,161 --> 00:45:00,101
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

967
00:45:00,101 --> 00:45:02,891
♪To know right from wrong♪

968
00:45:04,801 --> 00:45:08,331
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

969
00:45:08,331 --> 00:45:11,581
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

970
00:45:11,741 --> 00:45:17,501
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

971
00:45:17,921 --> 00:45:22,521
♪At just the right time♪
